lank. (These are legacy-Aura data-recordid links rendered in zero-width force-lookup cells — the alias must still be matched AND visible)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>CA-03</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Case alias</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Not duplicated</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Low</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A list that already has a Project column (Examiner Team / All)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Open it</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>No extra alias added — the existing Project column is left alone</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name=