templates targeted at EITHER team plus Global — and NOTHING from teams the user is not in. Admin if IsAdmin__c is set on any membership</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>S-06</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Security</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Single-team unchanged</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Low</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>User in exactly one team</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Connect; open the template menu</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Behaves exactly as before — their team&#x27;s templates + Global; identity shows the one team</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_section" table:number-columns-spanned="11" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:covered-table-cell table:number-columns-repeated="10"/></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-01</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Mark a controlled doc</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Medium</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Admin; a template</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Tick &#x27;Requires acknowledgement&#x27; on it; Save</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>It becomes a controlled document — an Acknowledge chip appears for members of its team(s)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-02</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Analyst acknowledges</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Medium</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Template ticked RequiresAck; member of its team</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Open it in the manager → click &#x27;I have read &amp; understood vX&#x27;</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Chip flips to &#x27;✓ Acknowledged&#x27;; banner count drops; a NucleusTemplateAck__c record is created (CreatedBy = you)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-03</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Re-ack on new version</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Medium</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Already acknowledged a controlled template</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Admin publishes a new version; re-sync</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Shows outstanding again — the old acknowledgement no longer matches the current version</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-04</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Admin matrix</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Medium</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Admin; some acknowledgements recorded</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Manager → Acknowledgements tab</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Per controlled template: acked/total + %, status, and the OUTSTANDING members&#x27; names — scoped to the template&#x27;s assigned team(s)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-05</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Outstanding nudge</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Low</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Outstanding controlled templates for you</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Trigger a background sync (SF tab open)</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>At most one browser notification per day; clicking it opens the manager</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>A-06</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Acknowledgements</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Not-yet-enabled message</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Low</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Ack object not deployed / In Development, or the user lacks Create on it</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Click &#x27;I have read &amp; understood vX&#x27;</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Friendly, actionable message that acknowledgements aren&#x27;t switched on yet (a template admin must finish setup) — NOT a raw &#x27;entity type cannot be inserted&#x27; error</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_result" table:content-validation-name="resultval" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p></text:p></table:table-cell></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_section" table:number-columns-spanned="11" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Suggestions</text:p></table:table-cell><table:covered-table-cell table:number-columns-repeated="10"/></table:table-row><table:table-row><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>S-07</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" office:value-type="string"><text:p>Suggestions</text:p></table:table-cell><table:table-cell table:style-name="ce_norm" of